room_title: Escape room "Live Free or Die" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: This was a ton of fun! The "live free or die" room was the one we solved and it wasn't easy. Took contributions from the whole group. It was a blast and when the "jail break" room comes up we will be back. We'll worth the money and time for a blast of fun! Pun intended!
